          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1637067255279-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>curry powder</strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> of the <strong>coconut stock</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a large mixing bowl (save the rest of the coconut stock for later!)</p><p>Add the <strong>tofu cubes</strong>, mix well and set aside</p>",
