    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> peanut butter</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>remaining coconut stock</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to a pot over a medium-low heat</p><p>Cook<strong> </strong>for approx. 15-20 min or until it has reduced to the consistency of a thick custard, stirring occasionally – this is your <strong>satay sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1637067282842-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1637067282842-x400.jpg",
