            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways then scrape out and discard the seeds using a teaspoon</p><p>Slice the <strong>cucumber</strong> <strong>halves</strong> finely</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>finely</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1637067310360-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
