            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> tofu satay skewers</strong> over the<strong> brown rice</strong> with the <strong>quick-pickled</strong> <strong>cucumber </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>satay sauce</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
